room_title: Escape room "Carcel" by Escape Room Delaware in Dover
room_description: You and your friends are part of the largest cartel in Mexico. You were indicted and arrested for money laundering and bribery. Your cellmate informed you he has plans to escape tomorrow. But, he was suddenly put in the hole before disclosing plans. You have 60 minutes to find his plans and escape before correctional staff removes his possessions!
